
Doxygen Documentation
---------------------

c++ http://www.doxygen.nl/manual/docblocks.html

To create doxy file:

doxygen -g



Changes:

- PROJECT_NAME           = "templateGLibrary"
- PROJECT_NUMBER         =
- EXTRACT_PRIVATE        = YES (change to NO show just the public interface)
- OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_FOR_C  = YES
- BUILTIN_STL_SUPPORT    = YES
- PROJECT_BRIEF          = "templateGLibrary Library Framework"
- QUIET                  = YES
- RECURSIVE              = YES
- EXCLUDE                = README.md \
                          .git \
                          html \
						  example.cc
- EXCLUDE_PATTERNS       = *moc*
- SOURCE_BROWSER         = YES
- HTML_COLORSTYLE_SAT    = 50
- HTML_TIMESTAMP         = YES
